'''Lorshan Pass''' was an area of volcanic caverns on [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]]. During the [[Summertime War]] it was the location of an [[Upland Liberation Front]] headquarters and [[Korun/Legends|Korunnai]] refugee camp, and contained a [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] transmitter. It was located 50 [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] southeast of [[Oran Mas]], and was the site of the [[Battle of Lorshan Pass]].

